Document: ExternalTexture
Path: godot/classes/class_externaltexture.rst
Summary: Methods for retrieving and setting the external texture buffer ID.

Method: get_external_texture_id() → int. Const method. Returns the current external texture buffer ID.

Method: set_external_buffer_id(external_buffer_id: int) → void. Sets the external buffer ID for the texture. This is required to bind the texture to an external buffer in the rendering pipeline.
