Document: ExternalTexture
Path: godot/classes/class_externaltexture.rst
Summary: Methods for retrieving and setting external texture and buffer IDs used in platform-specific operations.

Method: get_external_texture_id() → int
Returns the external texture ID. Note: You may need to pass this to platform APIs when creating Android SurfaceTextures.

Method: set_external_buffer_id(external_buffer_id: int) → void
Sets the external buffer ID. Warning: You should call this with data received from platform APIs like SurfaceTexture.getHardwareBuffer() on Android.